Divides vocabulary into awareness category.

Level 3 : fully memorized

Level 2 : aware but lack retention

Level 1 : Cannot recall awareness


Vocabulary awareness evaluates in 2 categories
1. Long term memorization
2. Short term memorization

Long term memorization
    # correct / # tested
    Test process:
        Words lowest ranking test first
        Long term memorization records during

Work on time period algorithm

    Longer time period, greater effectiveness on memorization
Implementation on sets --> Work on a set of words after completing relative memorization

Frequency of category

    Practice Level 1 first --> level 2 --> level 3
        Test based on frequency
               Level 1 : 50%
               Level 2 : 30%
               Level 3 : 20%